snippet.title: Kirby’s Dream Buffet – Overview Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Pre-Order Now: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/kirbys-dream-buffet-switch/

Roll into this smorgasbord of fun with 3 other friends in local wireless or online! Or play with a buddy on the same system! Kirby's Dream Buffet releases on 8/17, exclusively on the Nintendo Switch system.

#Kirby #KirbysDreamBuffet #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot
